topic.title: Human Clinical Subject Data Document Sectioin - conformance rules

section.p: The document is divided into sections as defined by the user. It is reccomended that each section contain a single type of the possible listed templates. In the case of visit and pharmokinetic parameters, this allows for inclusion of data from other SDTM defined data structures (domain) to be included within the section. The user is also free to create custom sections based on the included generic templates: Study Subject Finding, Study Subject Event, Study Subject Intervention.
